title: Transferring my account back to EUW.
body:
I created my account on EUW. Now it's on NA for almost a year. 

I want to transfer it back to EUW. Will my champion mastery points and border override the old mastery points I earned when I played on EUW or it will revert back to where I left. 

Thanks

replies.body: It's okay if you've previously already had an account on a server you want to transfer to.  Everything included in the [Transfer FAQ](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/201751924-Account-Transfer-FAQ) still applies regardless.  The only thing that could possibly change is your username and summoner name, but everything else should remain the same per the faq.  Be sure to review it before making the change!  Hope that helps clarify some things!
